et/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%E1%BB%83n-ng%E1%BB%99/poem-2II7Zn7HolDWJm0WmyE2Xw">Khiển ngộ - 遣遇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Th%E1%BA%A3o-Ma-Sa-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-h%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-5tYkfou58rwK6U6abxfIIw">Thảo Ma Sa động hịch - 討麻沙洞檄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Th%E1%BA%BF-nan-dung/poem-YhukMB5bIecVu8b-KCIaQw">Thế nan dung - 世難容</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
